trative power, can run any code they like within Apple's private AI cloud, it would cost the company a lot more thank $1,000,000 to get everything fixed and regain consumer trust. So, feeling up to the task? If you don't feel like you can take on one of the biggest tech company's security, but you're still interested in ethical hacking, why not check out the Flipper Zero instead?",
